you have reached your Account Limit, or
you or the Account Manager have breached these Terms and Conditions, or
we are required to do so under any applicable law or regulation or at the direction of any regulatory, law enforcement, or other competent authority.
In the event that we do suspend or terminate your Account, we will inform you in advance if possible; otherwise, we will notify you immediately afterwards to the extent permitted by law.
